<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us - Organic Store</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/home.css">

    <style>
        :root {
            --green-dark:  #1a3c2e;
            --green-mid:   #2d6a4f;
            --green-light: #52b788;
            --green-pale:  #d8f3dc;
        }

        * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

        body {
            font-family: 'DM Sans', Arial, sans-serif;
            background: #f4f7f5;
            color: #1a3c2e;
            min-height: 100vh;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }

        /* ── HERO ── */
        .about-hero {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a3c2e 0%, #2d6a4f 60%, #52b788 100%);
            padding: 72px 24px 110px;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .about-hero::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -60px; right: -60px;
            width: 280px; height: 280px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: rgba(82,183,136,0.15);
        }
        .about-hero::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -80px; left: -40px;
            width: 220px; height: 220px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
        }
        .hero-badge {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 6px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.14);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.22);
            border-radius: 100px;
            padding: 6px 16px;
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.90);
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 500;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        .about-hero h1 {
            font-size: 2.8rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #fff;
            margin-bottom: 14px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        .about-hero p {
            font-size: 1.05rem;
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.78);
            max-width: 520px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .about-hero h1 { font-size: 2rem; }
        }

        /* ── WRAPPER ── */
        .about-wrapper {
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: -52px auto 60px;
            padding: 0 24px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
        }

        /* ── INTRO CARD ── */
        .intro-card {
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 32px rgba(26,60,46,0.10);
            padding: 48px 48px 40px;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 320px;
            gap: 48px;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }
        @media (max-width: 760px) {
            .intro-card {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                padding: 32px 24px;
                gap: 28px;
            }
        }
        .intro-text h2 {
            font-size: 1.6rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--green-dark);
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }
        .intro-text h2 span {
            color: var(--green-light);
        }
        .intro-text p {
            font-size: 15px;
            color: #4a6b58;
            margin-bottom: 14px;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }
        .intro-img {
            width: 100%;
            border-radius: 16px;
            overflow: hidden;
            background: var(--green-pale);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 24px;
            min-height: 200px;
        }
        .intro-img img {
            max-width: 100%;
            max-height: 220px;
            object-fit: contain;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        /* ── MISSION CARD ── */
        .mission-card {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--green-dark) 0%, var(--green-mid) 100%);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 44px 48px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .mission-card::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -40px; right: -40px;
            width: 180px; height: 180px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: rgba(82,183,136,0.18);
        }
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .mission-card { padding: 32px 24px; }
        }
        .mission-card .section-label {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 6px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.14);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.22);
            border-radius: 100px;
            padding: 5px 14px;
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.88);
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 500;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        .mission-card h2 {
            font-size: 1.6rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #fff;
            margin-bottom: 14px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        .mission-card p {
            font-size: 15px;
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.80);
            max-width: 680px;
            line-height: 1.8;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        /* ── WHY CHOOSE US ── */
        .why-section {
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 32px rgba(26,60,46,0.10);
            padding: 44px 48px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .why-section { padding: 32px 24px; }
        }
        .section-header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 36px;
        }
        .section-header .label-tag {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 6px;
            background: var(--green-pale);
            color: var(--green-mid);
            border-radius: 100px;
            padding: 5px 14px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }
        .section-header h2 {
            font-size: 1.6rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--green-dark);
        }

        .features-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
            gap: 16px;
        }
        @media (max-width: 580px) {
            .features-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        }

        .feature-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
            gap: 16px;
            padding: 20px;
            background: #f8fdf9;
            border-radius: 14px;
            border: 1.5px solid var(--green-pale);
            transition: border-color 0.18s, transform 0.18s;
        }
        .feature-item:hover {
            border-color: var(--green-light);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        .feature-icon {
            width: 44px;
            height: 44px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            background: var(--green-pale);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: var(--green-mid);
            font-size: 16px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }
        .feature-text strong {
            display: block;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--green-dark);
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }
        .feature-text span {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #6b8a78;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        /* ── CLOSING BANNER ── */
        .closing-banner {
            background: var(--green-pale);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 40px 48px;
            text-align: center;
            border: 1.5px solid #b7e4c7;
        }
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .closing-banner { padding: 32px 24px; }
        }
        .closing-banner .leaf-icon {
            width: 56px;
            height: 56px;
            border-radius: 16px;
            background: var(--green-light);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 22px;
            margin: 0 auto 20px;
        }
        .closing-banner p {
            font-size: 15px;
            color: #4a6b58;
            max-width: 580px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }
        .closing-banner p strong {
            color: var(--green-dark);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <%- include("../../views/partials/user/header") %>

    <!-- HERO -->
    <div class="about-hero">
        <div class="hero-badge">
            <i class="fas fa-leaf" style="font-size:12px;"></i> Our Story
        </div>
        <h1>About Us</h1>
        <p>We believe in the power of nature to provide the purest, healthiest, and most sustainable products.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="about-wrapper">

        <!-- INTRO CARD -->
        <div class="intro-card">
            <div class="intro-text">
                <h2>Welcome to <span>Organic Store</span></h2>
                <p>
                    At <strong>Organic Store</strong>, we believe in the power of nature to provide the purest, healthiest,
                    and most sustainable products. Founded with a mission to bring the best organic goods to your doorstep,
                    we work directly with local farmers and trusted suppliers to ensure every item meets our rigorous quality standards.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Our store offers a wide range of organic fruits, vegetables, dairy, and pantry staples.
                    Everything we sell is free from harmful chemicals, synthetic fertilizers, and GMOs,
                    so you can shop with confidence for your family.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="intro-img">
                <img src="/images/organic-store-white-logo.png" alt="Organic Farm" />
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- MISSION CARD -->
        <div class="mission-card">
            <div class="section-label">
                <i class="fas fa-seedling" style="font-size:11px;"></i> Our Mission
            </div>
            <h2>Promoting Health &amp; Sustainability</h2>
            <p>
                We are committed to promoting health, sustainability, and community. By choosing organic, you're not only
                caring for your well-being but also supporting eco-friendly practices and fair-trade principles.
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- WHY CHOOSE US -->
        <div class="why-section">
            <div class="section-header">
                <div class="label-tag">
                    <i class="fas fa-star" style="font-size:11px;"></i> Why Choose Us
                </div>
                <h2>What Sets Us Apart</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="features-grid">
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <div class="feature-icon"><i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt"></i></div>
                    <div class="feature-text">
                        <strong>Locally Sourced</strong>
                        <span>Fresh, locally sourced organic products straight from trusted farmers near you.</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <div class="feature-icon"><i class="fas fa-box-open"></i></div>
                    <div class="feature-text">
                        <strong>Eco-Friendly Packaging</strong>
                        <span>All our packaging is biodegradable and designed to minimize environmental impact.</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <div class="feature-icon"><i class="fas fa-certificate"></i></div>
                    <div class="feature-text">
                        <strong>Quality &amp; Sustainability</strong>
                        <span>Dedicated to the highest quality standards with a focus on sustainable practices.</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <div class="feature-icon"><i class="fas fa-headset"></i></div>
                    <div class="feature-text">
                        <strong>Exceptional Service</strong>
                        <span>Our friendly customer support team is always ready to assist you at every step.</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- CLOSING BANNER -->
        <div class="closing-banner">
            <div class="leaf-icon"><i class="fas fa-leaf"></i></div>
            <p>
                Thank you for choosing <strong>Organic Store</strong>. Together, let's make healthier choices
                and nurture the planet for future generations.
            </p>
        </div>

    </div>

    <%- include("../../views/partials/user/footer") %>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>
</html>